summary: You know what I just realized?  Rick from Rick and Morty is basically a Mary Sue and yet he is loved by the same people who...
body:
You know what I just realized?  Rick from Rick and Morty is basically a Mary Sue and yet he is loved by the same people who complains that characters like Rey from Star Wars or Captain Marvel (despite the film not even being out yet) are/will be Mary Sues and that’s apparently bad.

Don’t get me wrong, I love Rick and Morty and Rick Sanchez as a character,  But I find the hypocrisy interesting.
